snippet.title: Fit My Cat  | Gameplay Trailer | XboX One Series S|X
snippet.description:
Fit My Cats is a 2D logical game with cute, hand-drawn illustrations. You can train your imagination and also check your space management skills.

Check out on the Xbox Store: https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/Fit-My-Cat/9NK8CMH7G1SV
Available now on the Nintendo eShop: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/fit-my-cat-switch/

Don't forget to follow us on 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/RedDeer_Games
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/RedDeerGames
and Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/reddeer_games/
